CONTENTS &#183; BIBLIOGRAPHIC RECORD







Gerard Manley Hopkins (1844&#150;89).  Poems.  1918.
 
52.  Summa
  









 
THE BEST ideal is the true
  And other truth is none.
All glory be ascrib&egrave;d to
  The holy Three in One.


 See Notes.

 











