With a so&uacute;th-w&eacute;sterly w&iacute;nd bl&uacute;stering, with a tide rolls reels
Of crumbling, fore-foundering, thundering all-surfy seas in; seen        5
&Uacute;nderneath, their glassy barrel, of a fairy green.   .   .   .   .   .   .   .   .
Or a jaunting vaunting vaulting assaulting trumpet telling


