63. 'The furl of fresh-leaved dogrose down'. Hopkins, Gerard Manley. 1918. Poems






.FormLt1	{	font-family:		arial, helvetica;
				font-size:			12px;
				color:				#000000;
				font-weight:		normal;
				background-color:	#ffffff; }
